ps://web.archive.org/web/20161220063621/http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/france-silverwave-grabs-gold-in-grand-prix-de-saint-cloud/2112462/international/ |archivedate= 2016-12-20 }}</ref>。巨橙在英國成功衛冕[[太子妃錦標|太子妃錦標]]以及[[古活盃|古活盃]]<ref>{{cite news |first= Wihtshire |last= Alex |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Orange battles to retainGoodwood Cup crown |url= http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/goodwood-big-orange-battles-to-second-cup-success/2127242/top/ |work=  |publisher= [[Racing_Post|Racing Post]] |date= 2016-07-28 |accessdate= 2016-12-05 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20161220063840/http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/goodwood-big-orange-battles-to-second-cup-success/2127242/top/ |archivedate= 2016-12-20 }}</ref>兩項二級賽。里見皇冠最好的成績在[[京都紀念賽|京都紀念賽]]大勝而回。喜蓮歡星在今年的[[香港金盃|香港金盃]]力戰之下跑亞軍。更凌駕於今年4月贏出夏葛特錦標。以身犯難在凱旋門大賽後贏出[[巴黎市議會大賽|巴黎市議會大賽]]<ref>{{cite news |first= Fougeray |last= Francis |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Prix du Conseil de Paris : One Foot In Heaven : un Conseil et un Vase |url= http://www.paris-turf.com/actualites/prix-du-conseil-de-paris-one-foot-in-heaven-un-conseil-et-un-vase-142364-142364?id=142364 |work=  |publisher= [[Paris-Turf|Paris-Turf]] |date= 2016-10-16 |accessdate= 2016-12-05 |archive-date= 2018-09-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180927043113/http://www.paris-turf.com/actualites/prix-du-conseil-de-paris-one-foot-in-heaven-un-conseil-et-un-vase-142364-142364?id=142364 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。克丘亞是2014年[[新加坡金盃|新加坡金盃]]冠軍<ref>{{cite news |first= Lee |last= Michael |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Shaw punches home second 1-2 in Gold Cup |url= http://www.turfclub.com.sg/MediaCenter/RacingNews/Pages/LocalDetails.aspx?intNewsID=13062&spListName=Local%20News&Year=2014#.WEVCmX3CflJ |work=  |publisher= [[新加坡賽馬公會|新加坡賽馬公會]] |date= 2014-11-16 |accessdate= 2016-12-05 |archive-date= 2018-10-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181003024810/http://www.turfclub.com.sg/MediaCenter/RacingNews/Pages/LocalDetails.aspx?intNewsID=13062&spListName=Local%20News&Year=2014#.WEVCmX3CflJ |dead-url= no }}</ref>，這是練馬師紹爾回家鄉南非養病前最後一次派馬出賽<ref>{{cite news |first= Lee |last= Michael |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Quechua gets late call-up for Hong Kong |url= http://www.turfclub.com.sg/MediaCenter/RacingNews/Pages/LocalDetails.aspx?intNewsID=15569&spListName=Local%20News&Year=2016#.WEVDBX3CflI |work=  |publisher= [[新加坡賽馬公會|新加坡賽馬公會]] |date= 2014-11-29 |accessdate= 2016-12-05 |archive-date= 2018-10-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181003033118/http://www.turfclub.com.sg/MediaCenter/RacingNews/Pages/LocalDetails.aspx?intNewsID=15569&spListName=Local%20News&Year=2016#.WEVDBX3CflI |dead-url= no }}</ref>。火紅人曾贏出三級賽[[一月盃|一月盃]]。紐西蘭馬奔勝力2016年5至6月遠征澳洲時贏出[[布里斯本盃|布里斯本盃]]，如麥露絲落實策騎，她是首位女騎師在香港國際賽事中策騎馬匹出賽。東方快車在11月的婦女銀袋賽跑第三，首次在分級賽上名。曾經有咬其他馬匹習慣的期惑，在同場同程的[[皇太后紀念盃|皇太后紀念盃]]取得亞軍。新紀錄去年在香港盃跑得亞軍，上戰在美國取下勝利<ref>{{cite news |first=  |last=  |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Nuovo Record Scores in Red Carpet Handicap |url= http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/217948/nuovo-record-scores-in-red-carpet-handicap |work=  |publisher= [[Blood-Horse|Blood-Horse]] |date= 2016-11-24 |accessdate= 2016-12-05 |archive-date= 2016-11-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161127052919/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/217948/nuovo-record-scores-in-red-carpet-handicap |dead-url= no }}</ref>。醒目層次在雌馬賽事中有不錯表現，這是牠首次在一級賽與雄馬交手。

