-10-22 |accessdate= 2016-12-05 |archive-date= 2016-12-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161220170246/http://www.news.com.au/sport/superracing/vic-racing/rebel-dane-wins-manikato-stakes-as-chautauqua-fails-and-buffering-retires/news-story/2bb383b702dc3cfab8fab87222404782 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。福兆在紀爾斯大賽中輕鬆贏馬<ref>{{cite news |first= Manley |last= Michael |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Blessing wins dramatic Prix Maurice de Gheest |url= http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/france-signs-of-blessing-lands-maurice-de-gheest/2133242/top/ |work=  |publisher= [[Racing_Post|Racing Post]] |date= 2016-08-14 |accessdate= 2016-12-05 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20161220215518/http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/france-signs-of-blessing-lands-maurice-de-gheest/2133242/top/ |archivedate= 2016-12-20 }}</ref>，在英國的[[鑽禧錦標|鑽禧錦標]]亦勇奪季軍。彎刀赤駿在短途馬錦標憑後上險勝，初奪一級賽。龍城勇將在主席短途獎爆冷跑入季軍。轟鳴在英國冠軍短途錦標爆冷跑第二後，在11月初贏出表列賽溫特沃斯錦標。記錄在案在贏出冬盡錦標後隨即以替補身份加入戰團<ref>{{cite news |first= Di Iorio |last= Carl |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Moore's Winterbottom delight with Takedown |url= https://www.racing.com/news/2016-11-26/moores-winterbottom-delight-with-takedown |work=  |publisher= racing.com |date= 2016-11-26 |accessdate= 2016-12-05 |archive-date= 2016-12-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161220101205/https://www.racing.com/news/2016-11-26/moores-winterbottom-delight-with-takedown |dead-url= no }}</ref>。純知覺今年在美國於草地短途三級賽取得二連捷。積多福遠征南韓時贏出韓國短途錦標，首次在遠征外地取下勝利。

