步步友是2014年香港一哩錦標冠軍，去年在此賽事取得季軍，在該賽後長期休息<ref>{{cite news |first= Cox |last= Michael |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Hong Kong Horse of the Year Able Friend sidelined for rest of the season |url= http://www.scmp.com/sport/racing/article/1898587/hong-kongs-horse-year-able-friend-sidelined-rest-season |work=  |publisher= [[南華早報|南華早報]] |date= 2016-01-07 |accessdate= 2016-12-05 |archive-date= 2016-03-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160307230644/http://www.scmp.com/sport/racing/article/1898587/hong-kongs-horse-year-able-friend-sidelined-rest-season |dead-url= no }}</ref>。去年挑戰失敗的詠彩繽紛在[[女皇銀禧紀念盃|女皇銀禧紀念盃]]取勝。標誌名駒於2016年的安田紀念賽中一放到底擊敗滿樂時。大印銀紙在香港一哩錦標奪亞後贏出董事盃。美麗大師上場在馬會一哩錦標後上險勝<ref>{{cite news |first= Morgan |last= David |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= 「美麗大師」攻下「中銀理財」馬會一哩錦標 |url= http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2016-11/news_2016112001812.html |work=  |publisher= [[香港賽馬會|香港賽馬會]] |date= 2016-11-21 |accessdate= 2016-12-05 |archive-date= 2016-12-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161220092409/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2016-11%2Fnews_2016112001812.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。喜蓮獎星贏出三級賽[[精英碟|精英碟]]，是本年香港國際賽事中唯一代表香港的雄馬。新寫實派在札幌紀念賽擊敗了滿樂時。包裝奔馳在上季有所進步，並在冠軍一哩賽取得季軍。美麗之星在去年贏出馬會一哩錦標。巨獅嶺今年表現轉好，贏出二級賽[[喬爾錦標|喬爾錦標]]。醒目名駒在上戰馬會一哩錦標跑獲亞軍，是至今分級賽最好表現。神燈光照2016年分別贏出京王盃春季盃以及天鵝錦標。首飾太陽四歲時攻下[[香港經典一哩賽|香港經典一哩賽]]及[[香港經典盃|香港經典盃]]。壯思飛在2016-17年馬季開始不久憑輕磅之利攻下[[慶典盃|慶典盃]]<ref>{{cite news |first= Morgan |last= David |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= 「壯思飛」勝出慶典盃 |url= http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2016-10/news_2016100101816.html |work=  |publisher= [[香港賽馬會|香港賽馬會]] |date= 2016-10-01 |accessdate= 2016-12-05 |archive-date= 2016-12-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161220092224/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2016-10%2Fnews_2016100101816.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

